{"tid":1824092,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[人人都是BACKUP師] youtube-dl-gui, 支援youtube facebook Instagram等","createTime":"2020-01-14T07:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T17:03:53.000Z","uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4d26d0bd71ee58e3c8a74256355d8d4ff0bad45f","tid":1824092,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:50:09.000Z","msg":"軟件名稱: youtube-dl-gui<br />\n支援youtube facebook Instagram streamable等<br />\n<br />\n網址:<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/MrS0m30n3/youtube-dl-gui/releases\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FMrS0m30n3%2Fyoutube-dl-gui%2Freleases&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSernr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=81fafee4\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/MrS0m30n3/youtube-dl-gui/releases</a><br />\n可以見到 <code>\nyoutube-dl-gui-0.4-win-portable.zip\n</code><br />\ndownload佢, 解壓縮<br />\n入去folder入面, 見到 <code>youtube-dl-gui.exe</code>, double click開啟軟件<br />\n<br />\n第一次用前, <em><ins>一定要click 右上角個gear icon, 禁  <code>update</code></ins></em><br />\n之後將你要download既片既網址paste係入面, 禁右手邊 <code>add</code><br />\n揀要download去咩folder, 再禁右下角  <code>download icon</code><br />\n支援呢堆網址:<br />\n<a href=\"https://ytdl-org.github.io/youtube-dl/supportedsites.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fytdl-org.github.io%2Fyoutube-dl%2Fsupportedsites.html&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSernr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=d4b3637d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ytdl-org.github.io/youtube-dl/supportedsites.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>無拿拿有日用唔到既時候, 再update就應該用得返</ins><br />\n<br />\nBACKUP師全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75fc6a09b83a69afbd44eb3af2a967528fe36f3c","tid":1824092,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T08:06:56.000Z","msg":"提一提<br />\nbackup youtube片都會計落 view count<br />\n如果你想backup d 閪片, 例如陳怡D垃撚圾言論<br />\n<br />\n就要click右上角個gear icon, click  <code>options</code><br />\nclick入  <code>Extra</code> tab , 係youtube-dl command line options 入面打  <code>--no-mark-watched</code>"},{"pid":"2305fad1fefa3d854f09bebc97dc52b642d6550d","tid":1824092,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T08:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VwQfCV5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVwQfCV5.gif&h=82755c39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c64b75f92b82053cba656baf67c2064f158d9ef","tid":1824092,"uid":97551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"facd924f32edf529cb03e6b028c8ad45f52d316a","tid":1824092,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:41:25.000Z","msg":"竟然有負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f28317f162d7e26dfdc101305c4747af58b010","tid":1824092,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:39:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14b30abb36e50610dd7af97be4bc1455db654a8c","tid":1824092,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:47:21.000Z","msg":"隻app你寫？"},{"pid":"7561b8fff4c0db88a6b595f9b6c22f61639202a0","tid":1824092,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14b30abb36e50610dd7af97be4bc1455db654a8c","tid":1824092,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:47:21.000Z","msg":"隻app你寫？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T18:15:06.000Z","msg":"no<br />\n佢base on youtube-dl, 好出名既CLI app<br />\n用左好耐"},{"pid":"5528a30ec9c15eff2e246dc30dedd3f956b01f2a","tid":1824092,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7561b8fff4c0db88a6b595f9b6c22f61639202a0","tid":1824092,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"